message.body: Hi! This is Katelyn, the singer who emailed you from craigslist. Sorry it's taken me a few days to get back to you- I was out of the state. I'm back now and am up for meeting and singing whenever you're free! :)
hey thanks. what's your availability like?
It's pretty flexible, i have an internships and some gigs so not much week to week. i can't do thursday afternoons/evenings or saturday from 6:30 to 8:30, but otherwise it varies!
Weekdays or weekends better for you?
Great. Do you live in the city?
I'm in havertown, so just outside of the city
Ohok. I live in Fairmount right next to art museum
Awesome, that's not far from me at all! :D
